{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">Q4250</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$10.40 – $10.40 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">1</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">10 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">1</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$10.40 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Apparel Color and Size</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/0/1/011DDCE01AFB040778290FB5A2331599.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795500</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Black</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/8/3/83073622BEA663016E63CDA38929C1AA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795540</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Forest</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/6/D/6D5EFFC865E0A353EF0C42BC83F40BCC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795240</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Natural</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/2/6/2668D7C62E3BAF7AF5043D4458C1C417.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795650</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Navy</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/B/E/BE1E0816264B4CC32D93DA45D3C22329.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795700</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Red</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/D/7/D7C6AF3F34BD504E9C793029889B89B0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795750</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Royal</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/C/1CFD49A6C186EB2B71B54036FE56FBCC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">B45795000</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">White</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$10.40 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Full-Length Apron with Pouch Pocket - Q4250. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">Q4250</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>10 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">1</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}